Name: Sales Type
Expression:
IF(
    CONTAINSSTRING( InTrans_Unique[DESCRIPTION], "Inv No." ),
    "Work Order",
    "Over the Counter"
)

Name: Sales Type
Expression:
VAR _DescText = 
    CALCULATE(
        MAX( InTrans_Unique[DESCRIPTION] ),
        FILTER(
            InTrans_Unique,
            InTrans_Unique[REF_NO] = Invoice[document_no]
        )
    )
RETURN
    IF(
        CONTAINSSTRING( _DescText, "Inv No."),
        "Work Order",
        "Over the Counter"
    )
